data.description: Welcome home! Beautiful and spacious end unit townhome in the gated community of Williams Preserve. Perfect for first time home buyers or investors as it is long term, short term, or Air B&B approved. This comfortable and inviting home features 2,014 Sq.Ft. of living space, 4 bedrooms, and 3 full bathrooms. As you walk into the home you'll find an inviting foyer with high ceiling and plenty of natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, living, and dinning areas. Sliding doors in the living room open to a covered, screened-in lanai, perfect for entertaining family and friends. One of the bedrooms is located in the first floor adjacent to a full bathroom, perfect for guests or a home office. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances, 42 inches height cabinets, closet pantry, and a big island with plenty of counter and seating space. Additional storage space under the stairs. Tile flooring throughout the main living areas on the first floor. The additional 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and closet laundry are conviniently located upstairs. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and en-suite bath with tiled walk-in shower and temperature controlled shower head system. NO CDD!! HOA covers gate access, playground, pool maintenance, exterior grounds, and lawn pest control. Williams Preserve is conveniently located close to Hwy 27, US 192, I-4, shopping, hospitals, amusement parks, Orlando International Airport, great dinning options and much more. Don't miss out on this opportunity...Make your appointment TODAY!
